{"tid":1531700,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有無人有時好似活係平行時空咁，覺得抗爭完左","createTime":"2019-09-02T10:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T10:51:02.000Z","uid":47208,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e76ee9359ab2caab756353da1156c2e73ecc26f0","tid":1531700,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:04:48.000Z","msg":"有無人平日覺得好似活係平行時空咁，覺得抗爭完左？<br />\n<br />\n其實反映到香港人抗爭係幾咁和平<br />\n一邊可以強烈表達訴求；另一邊影響唔到日常生活<br />\n<br />\n特別係唔經常上街遊行果班，<br />\n慢慢會好易覺得變淡無乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家要堅持每晚10點係窗邊嗌口號<br />\n呢種唔係左膠式抗爭，因為星期六日仲係要你出黎嫁！<br />\n<br />\n只係，<span style=\"color: orange;\">當每晚都聽到唔識既同路人係窗邊一齊納喊，<br />\n其實真係感受到民主路上並不孤單</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n22:00 、22:15 、 22:30<br />\n香港人，窗邊見<br />\n<br />\n香港加油已經嗌左一個月，不如我地一齊再改變心態？<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人，必勝</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人，必勝！"},{"pid":"c9f0d40c529b8fe868e42f7de7ed722d364b3153","tid":1531700,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:05:27.000Z","msg":"香港人，必勝！"},{"pid":"abaf0f238814b475a745a1847d055af5e6b9f4a6","tid":1531700,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:06:05.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f70cb124407dfa318e0b70e4a34beabccb0221","tid":1531700,"uid":21572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:06:53.000Z","msg":"10點大叫係keep hot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787ba40c5e21a90cbba93df3ff4a1b0936d14e44","tid":1531700,"uid":256632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"【持續更新】香港人九月日程表<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kEaguAX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kEaguAX</a>"},{"pid":"537e2800f453ddd2cba1fe26c3539e62fd8bde66","tid":1531700,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:27:30.000Z","msg":"9月1日頭：陳方被截追問，問到口啞啞！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531113</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4440015e59aa091f472b334faef5936b8e25ae4c","tid":1531700,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43f70cb124407dfa318e0b70e4a34beabccb0221","tid":1531700,"uid":21572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:06:53.000Z","msg":"10點大叫係keep hot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"香港人加油！"},{"pid":"5fe66edc330510cca96fb86efd6a93a07a3eb058","tid":1531700,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjtpsoQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjtpsoQ.gif&h=c1aba121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdd4815329762d52fdee22ac404a1555a026aa24","tid":1531700,"uid":7738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe66edc330510cca96fb86efd6a93a07a3eb058","tid":1531700,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjtpsoQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjtpsoQ.gif&h=c1aba121&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">每次見到都好感慨</code></pre>"},{"pid":"dd673842b81c9a327d0dc75386c2a6d73c65fa6d","tid":1531700,"uid":267791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"民主唔係淨係9嗌就有<br />\n不過都要你地繼續嗌 唔好嗌到變左左膠mode<br />\n<br />\n除左嗌 唔該做多d實事<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">(手動複製貼上，貼得九月你就做)\n\n和理非，好無力，好忟？\n要抗爭，只有十月一前每日堅持做以下既事，係堅持，堅唔到都要堅，係呢到發誓你堅持呢個九月，就一個月：\n\n1. 罷消費（任何福建幫、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、藍紅食店）好難？勇武難唔難？\n2. 低享樂（要發洩，做運動、十點9叫、唔好taobao消費食好野）\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）\n4. 每日like and share 1個文宣post\n5. 下載Twitter 開acc,每日出1個post\n6. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣教育自由行。\n7. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣\n8. 出糧提款換美金\n9. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票\n10. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金\n11. 跳閘推閘\n12. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與\n\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。</code></pre>"},{"pid":"26534c6897a70f1f4ddc77f04d856efe30f512a3","tid":1531700,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"所以要吸納民意，令更多人用行動支持"},{"pid":"3ca2f1bcf5c2b7282985cd9ddff9825054f0326f","tid":1531700,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"個個星期一至四都係咁架啦<br />\n然後到星期五就進入緊張狀態星期六日就開波<br />\n當然間唔中都會有突發事"},{"pid":"ba6f30b9ff19e0573b9ec165a8c766aae5a5aa7b","tid":1531700,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"必勝!"},{"pid":"f7e09d4350ad97d296cb131eb961c460a76a8230","tid":1531700,"uid":102089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"未完 重有排玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLbOTrA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLbOTrA.png&h=df19bfe5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}